{"tid":93833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真問］有關申請公屋問題","createTime":"2017-01-24T17:21:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T17:43:10.000Z","uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0aca157fb1b17a100ab5d9c64101749b14c97f92","tid":93833,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:21:36.000Z","msg":"係咁既，因為屋企一啲家事，家道中落。宜家暫時住係親戚屋企 親戚屋企係公屋，咁我想申請公屋就自然唔可以填佢個地址喇。<br />\n由於我親戚屋企塞唔落咁多人，我就搬左去同男朋友住，佢果到居屋，唔知補左地價未。<br />\n如果我用佢個地址申請又得唔得呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?<br />\n<br />\n求解答 連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fe2c920d01533af4b72d50191a8c5e82563870","tid":93833,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:24:42.000Z","msg":"正常無問題 但單身排公屋十年都未必上到，或者考慮結婚再生多一個咁就幾年內可以上樓"},{"pid":"91d8c457eca76d5de6f84218c54faa1b022c9cae","tid":93833,"uid":18313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:30:50.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"ee174b4915660b2c1db07aed281b3c1d09cd599f","tid":93833,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常無問題 但單身排公屋十年都未必上到，或者考慮結婚再生多一個咁就幾年內可以上樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我諗住填埋我呀媽個名一齊排<br />\n但我就咁同居報上去唔算犯法架可？"},{"pid":"f91bbfc453c0e54c74e09403746346baa5afbc33","tid":93833,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可以</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我驚咁樣係犯法 因為唔知居屋住唔住得外人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1947a006ff254d6cf64de7d4b80e056996348405","tid":93833,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ef2649346814949c2bde2fc0ddeafb908e5ac82","tid":93833,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:31:26.000Z","msg":"你住址填半山都得 只要符合入息同資產要求"},{"pid":"4b1f3b5d661bdd5df18b7139104865714de41d3a","tid":93833,"uid":27568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"無補地價係唔可以租同賣俾人<br />\n可以住<br />\n<br />\n公屋果個只係通訊地址"},{"pid":"3717d67687b547805f1e2480f69a578299a92d13","tid":93833,"uid":550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我驚咁樣係犯法 因為唔知居屋住唔住得外人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n居屋理論上買咗就係私有財產<br />\n畀咩人住都得<br />\n補地價係你想賣層樓出去先要"},{"pid":"5b72d2b61f28b2407cc9c4d8e93916a412799d80","tid":93833,"uid":52671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T08:38:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可以</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我驚咁樣係犯法 因為唔知居屋住唔住得外人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n常識問題肥佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b76b22b9aec6367be052ceb2b2e137a87812002","tid":93833,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你住址填半山都得 只要符合入息同資產要求</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打 連登有愛"},{"pid":"3fa35dc4f8f9b24635240a42ad3c1a7e490363f6","tid":93833,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:19:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無補地價係唔可以租同賣俾人<br />\n可以住<br />\n<br />\n公屋果個只係通訊地址</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我就係知唔可以租俾人 所以驚佢當我租人地方住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9284fcd56b740dddf1f8406436ad8f3bf0ee6e2e","tid":93833,"uid":39924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:19:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可以</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我驚咁樣係犯法 因為唔知居屋住唔住得外人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n常識問題肥佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ffcfe921f79e5016def28bc4065d4b038fadaa5","tid":93833,"uid":2997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:43:10.000Z","msg":"叫你男友同你簽左紙再去排家庭輪候會唔會快d?"}]}